          "rangeStart": 1466,
          "rangeEnd": 1727,
          "markText": "The cot the man lay on was in the wide shade of a mimosa tree and as he looked out past the shade onto the glare of the plain there were three of the big birds squatted obscenely,while in the sky a dozen more sailed, making quick-moving shadows as they passed.",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1778913588,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-05-16 14:39:48",
          "chapterUid": 59,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=918925&chapterUid=59&rangeStart=1466&rangeEnd=1727",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/032321005e058d032bdafe2?chapterUid=59&rangeStart=1466&rangeEnd=1727"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "918925_59_68022-68750",
          "range": "68022-68750",
          "rangeStart": 68022,
          "rangeEnd": 68750,
          "markText": "No, he thought, when everything you do, you do too long, and do too late, you can't expect to find the people still there. The people all are gone. The party's over and you are with your hostess now.不，他心想，当你做每一件事都做得太久，做得太晚，你就不能指望人们还在那里。人们都走了。聚会结束了，你现在和你的女主人在一起。I'm getting as bored with dying as with everything else, he thought.他想，我厌倦了死亡，就像我厌倦了一切。“It's a bore,” he said out loud.“太无聊了，”他大声说道。“What is, my dear?”“亲爱的，是什么？”“Anything you do too bloody long.”",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1778808258,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-05-15 09:24:18",
          "chapterUid": 59,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=918925&chapterUid=59&rangeStart=68022&rangeEnd=68750",
